  - `prompts.py:109`: Fix Dev prompt says `Read the fix plan from reviews/fix-plan.md`
  
  The Architect writes to project root `fix-plan.md`, but the Fix Dev agent's system prompt instructs it to look in `reviews/fix-plan.md`. If the Fix Dev follows its prompt literally, it will read from the wrong path. This may be mitigated by the task_description in `fix_dev_node` which passes the correct path, but the system prompt contradicts it.

