  Produces `input_files: ['src/foo.py', 'tests/test_a.py']` — Python list repr with single quotes. This is not valid YAML. Valid YAML would be `[src/foo.py, tests/test_a.py]` (flow style) or use `- item` syntax. If the review agent copies this into its output file verbatim, the YAML frontmatter is malformed.

